      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 6,
      "text": "API Gateway\n& Load balancer\n\n - Routing \n- rate limiting \n- authentication",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "mmk0jEo1Tx4snS_Qfx53B",
      "originalText": "API Gateway\n& Load balancer\n\n - Routing \n- rate limiting \n- authentication",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.35
    },
    {
      "id": "2QNigeAo4UAZ-tOvHaoz0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 257.0466984978841,
      "y": 249.5203586463711,
      "width": 440.26667960631914,
      "height": 250,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [
        "OjbQMPIJmAlCOnx2dohXJ"
      ],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b1j",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1662900625,
      "version": 753,
      "versionNonce": 2000680831,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1772550196494,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Ability for users to create/remove\nschedules for jobs\n- Ability for users to see the history of the\nexecuted jobs with status\n- Support both one time and recurring\nschedules\n- Job gets executed within 5 minutes of the\nspecified time\n- Jobs can only be invoked via REST APIs.\nThe API needs to be idempotent",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Ability for users to create/remove schedules for jobs\n- Ability for users to see the history of the executed jobs with status\n- Support both one time and recurring schedules\n- Job gets executed within 5 minutes of the specified time\n- Jobs can only be invoked via REST APIs. The API needs to be idempotent",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
